    "description": "How to evaluate generative engine optimisation companies — genuine capability markers, provider types, and the six questions to ask before you hire.",
    "author": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "GEOoptimised",
      "url": "https://geooptimised.com",
      "logo": "https://geooptimised.com/icon-512.png"
